She just gestures to the table and around.

1068
00:45:27,460 --> 00:45:29,460
Life's been better.

1069
00:45:29,460 --> 00:45:32,460
I think it was better when I was in the iceberg.

1070
00:45:32,460 --> 00:45:34,460
A Ruthatar wasn't as bad as Orcus.

1071
00:45:34,460 --> 00:45:36,460
I mean, we're going to go ahead and compare.

1072
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:37,460
Reasonable.

1073
00:45:37,460 --> 00:45:40,460
Yeah, Ice Dragon, much more reasonable than...

1074
00:45:40,460 --> 00:45:42,460
He's a knowledge seeker, really.

1075
00:45:42,460 --> 00:45:43,460
Yeah.

1076
00:45:43,460 --> 00:45:44,460
I miss that guy.

1077
00:45:44,460 --> 00:45:45,460
Yeah.

1078
00:45:45,460 --> 00:45:46,460
These are my friends.

1079
00:45:46,460 --> 00:45:49,460
This is Yenbul.

1080
00:45:49,460 --> 00:45:50,460
Hello.

1081
00:45:50,460 --> 00:45:51,460
It's nice to meet you.

1082
00:45:51,460 --> 00:45:52,460
Telgir.

1083
00:45:52,460 --> 00:45:53,460
Jarmed.

1084
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:56,460
And Agath.

1085
00:45:56,460 --> 00:45:57,460
Greetings.

1086
00:45:57,460 --> 00:45:58,460
Hello.

1087
00:45:58,460 --> 00:46:01,460
Hello to all of you.

1088
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:05,460
You are not the same group as last.

1089
00:46:05,460 --> 00:46:08,460
I assume that's why you're here.

1090
00:46:08,460 --> 00:46:11,460
Yeah, that is why we're here.

1091
00:46:11,460 --> 00:46:14,460
So we need your help.

1092
00:46:14,460 --> 00:46:15,460
I figured as much.

1093
00:46:15,460 --> 00:46:16,460
It's a long journey.

1094
00:46:16,460 --> 00:46:17,460
All right.

1095
00:46:17,460 --> 00:46:19,460
So we got the amulet.

1096
00:46:19,460 --> 00:46:25,460
I rifle through my bag and I procure it.

1097
00:46:25,460 --> 00:46:31,460
And what now?

1098
00:46:31,460 --> 00:46:39,460
Well, the ritual, which...

1099
00:46:39,460 --> 00:46:42,460
She looks down at a book in front of her.

1100
00:46:42,460 --> 00:46:59,460
Says, well, the ritual has a great toll in that it requires a large amount of magic.

1101
00:46:59,460 --> 00:47:05,460
Do you...

1102
00:47:05,460 --> 00:47:08,460
How much do you know?

1103
00:47:08,460 --> 00:47:14,460
Bits and pieces from what we've been told.

1104
00:47:14,460 --> 00:47:19,460
Magic is killing the world, sucking the energy out of the world.

1105
00:47:19,460 --> 00:47:21,460
The gods are gone.

1106
00:47:21,460 --> 00:47:23,460
You guys happen to have one here.

1107
00:47:23,460 --> 00:47:24,460
Yeah.

1108
00:47:24,460 --> 00:47:27,460
I don't know for how much longer though.

1109
00:47:27,460 --> 00:47:32,460
The ritual is weakening.

1110
00:47:32,460 --> 00:47:36,460
We managed to...

1111
00:47:36,460 --> 00:47:41,460
She managed to shroud Icewind Dale.

1112
00:47:41,460 --> 00:47:55,460
So much so that Orcus in his original attack and onslaught did not recognize this place as inhabited.

1113
00:47:55,460 --> 00:48:05,460
Then he sent his followers to various remote regions looking for those to be converted.

1114
00:48:05,460 --> 00:48:11,460
Oriel was able to make them go away for a little while.

1115
00:48:11,460 --> 00:48:17,460
But after so many don't come back, he sends larger forces.

1116
00:48:17,460 --> 00:48:28,460
That's when she turned those blizzards, frigid cold, into what you see before you.

1117
00:48:28,460 --> 00:48:31,460
What you made your way through.

1118
00:48:31,460 --> 00:48:36,460
No easy feat for some of us.

1119
00:48:36,460 --> 00:48:38,460
The horde keeps getting larger.

1120
00:48:38,460 --> 00:48:54,460
People in the world keep using magic, which is drawing from now not only gods that they know or the earth that they draw their power from, but anything that's left.

1121
00:48:54,460 --> 00:49:12,460
And Oriel's power is one of the largest locations, fonts of magic and energy left in the world.

1122
00:49:12,460 --> 00:49:26,460
So what you're saying is if we do the ritual that needs to be done to separate Flint and Bort,

1123
00:49:26,460 --> 00:49:36,460
it's essentially going to end the protection you have here and perhaps Oriel.

1124
00:49:36,460 --> 00:49:48,460
I don't know if it will, but it will have a severe cost somewhere else.

1125
00:49:48,460 --> 00:49:50,460
Cool.

1126
00:49:50,460 --> 00:49:57,460
Is there a way we can fight Orcus and try to get real power back to the world?

1127
00:49:57,460 --> 00:49:59,460
Where did the gods go?

1128
00:49:59,460 --> 00:50:02,460
The gods have been imprisoned.

1129
00:50:02,460 --> 00:50:08,460
All right, so maybe like a jailbreak.

1130
00:50:08,460 --> 00:50:11,460
Yeah, yeah. One of those.

1131
00:50:11,460 --> 00:50:13,460
Sure.

1132
00:50:13,460 --> 00:50:15,460
Imprisoned by Orcus.

1133
00:50:15,460 --> 00:50:16,460
Yes.

1134
00:50:16,460 --> 00:50:18,460
Where?

1135
00:50:18,460 --> 00:50:20,460
We haven't found them yet.

1136
00:50:20,460 --> 00:50:26,460
We've been searching as many of the planes as we can.

1137
00:50:26,460 --> 00:50:32,460
The ethereal regions are vast and plenty.

1138
00:50:32,460 --> 00:50:40,460
If we knew where they were, we would get them, she says.

1139
00:50:40,460 --> 00:50:45,460
She begins looking and searching through the books on her table.

1140
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:52,460
She picks one up and says, this is a log of all the locations that we've been.

1141
00:50:52,460 --> 00:50:55,460
I can give it to you if...

1142
00:50:55,460 --> 00:50:56,460
Sure.

1143
00:50:56,460 --> 00:51:00,460
That's a task you would want to take.

1144
00:51:00,460 --> 00:51:02,460
How many do you have searching?

1145
00:51:02,460 --> 00:51:04,460
We had many.

1146
00:51:04,460 --> 00:51:15,460
The entirety of the Arcane Brotherhood, which was hundreds of wizards, were now down to three.

1147
00:51:15,460 --> 00:51:17,460
Hmm.

1148
00:51:17,460 --> 00:51:21,460
Well, you can actually do a lot with three.

1149
00:51:21,460 --> 00:51:23,460
Put that out there.

1150
00:51:23,460 --> 00:51:28,460
Also, could I get that ritual not saying I'm going to do it or anything, but...

1151
00:51:28,460 --> 00:51:34,460
Do you have a magic user amongst you?

1152
00:51:34,460 --> 00:51:37,460
Like a wizard specifically or...

1153
00:51:37,460 --> 00:51:45,460
Well, someone who can properly execute the ritual to the letter.

1154
00:51:45,460 --> 00:51:51,460
Oh, Leosen is really good with paperwork.

1155
00:51:51,460 --> 00:51:54,460
I'm sure he'll get this done.

1156
00:51:54,460 --> 00:51:56,460
Leosen's a monk.

1157
00:51:56,460 --> 00:51:57,460
I'm sure that there are wizards.

1158
00:51:57,460 --> 00:51:59,460
Doesn't mean he's not good at paperwork, though.

1159
00:51:59,460 --> 00:52:00,460
That's right.

1160
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:02,460
We have established he's very good at paperwork.

1161
00:52:02,460 --> 00:52:06,460
Just to save us the return trip, you give us the ritual.

1162
00:52:06,460 --> 00:52:11,460
We'll go find the gods or whatever we need to do, but we don't want to have to come back here.

1163
00:52:11,460 --> 00:52:14,460
And then go back again to where Flint is.

1164
00:52:14,460 --> 00:52:15,460
You understand?

1165
00:52:15,460 --> 00:52:20,460
Yeah, really, this would have saved us a trip if we had only had the ritual to begin with.

1166
00:52:20,460 --> 00:52:24,460
Well, ten years ago...

1167
00:52:24,460 --> 00:52:26,460
More.

1168
00:52:26,460 --> 00:52:30,460
You were supposed to go get the Amulet of Wonder and return.

1169
00:52:30,460 --> 00:52:34,460
I assume, like, how far gone is he?

1170
00:52:34,460 --> 00:52:36,460
It's not great.

1171
00:52:36,460 --> 00:52:38,460
I don't want to talk about it.

1172
00:52:38,460 --> 00:52:48,460
My concern is that the souls are so intertwined that completing this ritual may destroy one of them.

1173
00:52:48,460 --> 00:52:49,460
Noted.

1174
00:52:49,460 --> 00:52:53,460
Do you have a vessel for the other if they are to be intertwined?

1175
00:52:53,460 --> 00:52:56,460
Listen, we don't have everything figured out, obviously.

1176
00:52:56,460 --> 00:52:58,460
We're piecemealing this thing.

1177
00:52:58,460 --> 00:53:01,460
Okay.

1178
00:53:01,460 --> 00:53:03,460
I will give you the ritual.

1179
00:53:03,460 --> 00:53:05,460
Thank you.

1180
00:53:05,460 --> 00:53:10,460
She walks over to a shelf,

1181
00:53:10,460 --> 00:53:16,460
sorts through some scrolls and hands you one that's covered in dust.

1182
00:53:16,460 --> 00:53:23,460
She blows it off and unravels it, nods and hands it to you.

1183
00:53:23,460 --> 00:53:26,460
I put it in my bag.

1184
00:53:26,460 --> 00:53:29,460
Thanks, Macoth.

1185
00:53:29,460 --> 00:53:34,460
And hey, maybe we'll find the gods first.

1186
00:53:34,460 --> 00:53:37,460
And...

1187
00:53:37,460 --> 00:53:42,460
I was going to say everything will be okay, it won't, but you know, everything will be okay.

1188
00:53:42,460 --> 00:53:48,460
Yes, perhaps we can find the gods, we set them free, world saved.

1189
00:53:48,460 --> 00:53:50,460
I hope you're right.

1190
00:53:50,460 --> 00:53:55,460
You feel like a rumble in the earth.

1191
00:53:55,460 --> 00:53:57,460
What was that?

1192
00:53:57,460 --> 00:53:59,460
Oh.

1193
00:53:59,460 --> 00:54:04,460
That's a tremor of the barrier closing in.

1194
00:54:04,460 --> 00:54:07,460
Could we see Oriel?

1195
00:54:07,460 --> 00:54:09,460
You can go try to find her.

1196
00:54:09,460 --> 00:54:12,460
Anywhere in particular?

1197
00:54:12,460 --> 00:54:15,460
She is shrouded in the sea of moving ice.

1198
00:54:15,460 --> 00:54:17,460
Oh, okay.

1199
00:54:17,460 --> 00:54:23,460
You are more than welcome to go try to find her, but she has concealed this region,

1200
00:54:23,460 --> 00:54:31,460
and her paranoia has escalated and doesn't come out ever.

1201
00:54:31,460 --> 00:54:34,460
I mean, in her defense, it seems well founded.

1202
00:54:34,460 --> 00:54:36,460
Yeah.

1203
00:54:36,460 --> 00:54:40,460
You, Goliath.

1204
00:54:40,460 --> 00:54:46,460
You look like you have questions, too.

1205
00:54:46,460 --> 00:54:50,460
I seek the gods.

1206
00:54:50,460 --> 00:55:02,460
I seek my, my god, who I thought abandoned us so many years ago.

1207
00:55:02,460 --> 00:55:22,460
But if she is imprisoned, I seek a way to break those chains or a way to break Orcus.

1208
00:55:22,460 --> 00:55:32,460
If you find the gods, they will be able to help undo what Orcus has done.

1209
00:55:32,460 --> 00:55:39,460
But you have no further insight from all your hundreds of mages.

1210
00:55:39,460 --> 00:55:44,460
Other than that, they are imprisoned somewhere in all the planes of existence.

1211
00:55:44,460 --> 00:55:47,460
We know where they are not.

1212
00:55:47,460 --> 00:55:55,460
And that may give you and your group clue as to where they are.

1213
00:55:55,460 --> 00:55:58,460
That is more than I had before.

1214
00:55:58,460 --> 00:56:00,460
Thanks, Macoth.

1215
00:56:00,460 --> 00:56:03,460
I think...

1216
00:56:03,460 --> 00:56:06,460
Is there a place we can rest?

1217
00:56:06,460 --> 00:56:08,460
Of course.

1218
00:56:08,460 --> 00:56:09,460
Of course.

1219
00:56:09,460 --> 00:56:11,460
We'll put you up.

1220
00:56:11,460 --> 00:56:14,460
You can stay as long as you need.

1221
00:56:14,460 --> 00:56:20,460
Are you, are you traveling back by foot?

1222
00:56:20,460 --> 00:56:22,460
To wherever you need to go?

1223
00:56:22,460 --> 00:56:26,460
Where are you off to?

1224
00:56:26,460 --> 00:56:32,460
Um, the looks to Talgir and Yenbul.

1225
00:56:32,460 --> 00:56:36,460
It's like...

1226
00:56:36,460 --> 00:56:42,460
I think we're probably going to talk about it.

1227
00:56:42,460 --> 00:56:43,460
Yes, I...

1228
00:56:43,460 --> 00:56:44,460
There's a lot to discuss.

1229
00:56:44,460 --> 00:56:52,460
We have learned a lot in the last several hours, and we need to decide what we will do.

1230
00:56:52,460 --> 00:56:57,460
How we survive without using magic.

1231
00:56:57,460 --> 00:57:02,460
You can use it, but use it wisely.

1232
00:57:02,460 --> 00:57:04,460
Don't use it to start campfires.

1233
00:57:04,460 --> 00:57:10,460
Don't use it to heal wounds that will heal themselves.

1234
00:57:10,460 --> 00:57:13,460
Use it when it matters.

1235
00:57:13,460 --> 00:57:16,460
Will do.

1236
00:57:16,460 --> 00:57:19,460
Agath, are you...

1237
00:57:19,460 --> 00:57:22,460
What are you going to do now?

1238
00:57:22,460 --> 00:57:25,460
I seek the gods. It is simple.

1239
00:57:25,460 --> 00:57:27,460
Okay.

1240
00:57:27,460 --> 00:57:29,460
And yourselves?

1241
00:57:29,460 --> 00:57:32,460
I think we also seek the gods.

1242
00:57:32,460 --> 00:57:37,460
Good. Four swords better than one.

1243
00:57:37,460 --> 00:57:41,460
The whole reason I...

1244
00:57:41,460 --> 00:57:43,460
I'm doing any of this.

1245
00:57:43,460 --> 00:57:53,460
The reason we are here at this moment is to get what will hopefully save Flint.

1246
00:57:53,460 --> 00:57:56,460
How long is it going to take us to find the gods?

1247
00:57:56,460 --> 00:58:05,460
But how do we say that getting back to Flint to do a ritual that might not even work is worth the whole world?

1248
00:58:05,460 --> 00:58:07,460
If we can find the gods, they can help us.

1249
00:58:07,460 --> 00:58:09,460
We can use magic again.

1250
00:58:09,460 --> 00:58:12,460
We can get rid of Orcus.

1251
00:58:12,460 --> 00:58:15,460
And that would be saving Flint too.

1252
00:58:15,460 --> 00:58:18,460
Agath, are you going to join us?

1253
00:58:18,460 --> 00:58:21,460
I have no objections to this.

